						<p class="short-desc">1st Runner Up in EIC 2020. Automated urban agriculture solution from **SST**.</p>
					</div>
				</article>

				<article class="project-card" onclick="document.getElementById('modal-pico').showModal()">
					<div class="project-image" style="background-color: #e0f2fe;">
						<span class="tag">Embedded Systems</span>
