					</div>
				</article>
			</div>

			<dialog id="modal-pico" class="project-modal">
				<div class="modal-header">
					<h2>RP2350 High-Speed DAQ</h2>
					<button class="close-btn" onclick="this.closest('dialog').close()">&times;</button>
				</div>
				<div class="modal-body">
					<p><strong>Overview:</strong> Leveraging the dual-core **RP2350** and its **PIO** blocks to achieve nanosecond-precision timing for physics data capture.</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Interfaced with 8-channel 12-bit ADCs.</li>
						<li>Implemented UDP streaming for real-time monitoring.</li>
					</ul>
					<a href="https://github.com" class="btn-project">View GitHub Source</a>
				</div>
			</dialog>

			<dialog id="modal-eic" class="project-modal">
				<div class="modal-header">
					<h2>Indoor Farming System</h2>
					<button class="close-btn" onclick="this.closest('dialog').close()">&times;</button>
				</div>
				<div class="modal-body">
					<p><strong>Achievement:</strong> Awarded **1st Runner Up** at EIC 2020. This project used **human-centered design** to simplify sustainable urban farming.</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Automated nutrient and water dosing.</li>
						<li>Integrated pH, moisture, and light sensors.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</dialog>
		</main>
		<Footer />

		<script>
			// 1. Modal Backdrop Click-to-Close
			const dialogs = document.querySelectorAll('dialog');
			dialogs.forEach(dialog => {
				dialog.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
					if (e.target === dialog) {
						(dialog as HTMLDialogElement).close();
					}
				});
			});

			// 2. Fade-Up Intersection Observer
			const observerOptions = {
				threshold: 0.1,
				rootMargin: '0px 0px -50px 0px'
			};

			const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
				entries.forEach((entry) => {
					if (entry.isIntersecting) {
						entry.target.classList.add('reveal');
						observer.unobserve(entry.target);
					}
				});
			}, observerOptions);

			document.querySelectorAll('.project-card').forEach(card => {
				observer.observe(card);
			});
		</script>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	main { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 2rem; }
	.projects-hero { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
	.projects-hero h1 { color: #0056b3; font-size: 2.5rem; }

	.projects-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
		gap: 2.5rem;
	}

	/* --- FADE-UP CORE STYLES --- */
	.project-card {
		background: white;
		border-radius: 12px;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
		border-top: 5px solid #0056b3;
		cursor: pointer;
		
		/* Initial hidden state */
		opacity: 0;
		transform: translateY(40px);
		transition: 
			opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1), 
			transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1), 
			box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}

	/* Revealing state triggered by JS */
	.project-card.reveal {
		opacity: 1;
		transform: translateY(0);
	}

	/* Hover effect (ensures it doesn't conflict with animation) */
	.project-card.reveal:hover {
		transform: translateY(-8px);
		box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 86, 179, 0.15);
	}

	.project-image { height: 160px; padding: 1rem; }
	.tag { background: #0056b3; color: white; padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: bold; }
	.project-content { padding: 1.5rem; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.6; }
	.tech-label { font-family: monospace; color: #0056b3; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

	/* Modal Styles */
	dialog {
		border: none;
		border-radius: 16px;
		padding: 0;
		width: 90%;
		max-width: 600px;
		box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
		border-top: 8px solid #0056b3;
	}
	dialog::backdrop {
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
		backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
	}
	.modal-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; background: #f8f9fa; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
	.modal-body { padding: 2rem; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.7; }
	.close-btn { background: none; border: none; font-size: 2rem; cursor: pointer; color: #999; }
	.btn-project { display: block; background: #0056b3; color: white; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; padding: 0.8rem; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
</style>